          "rubric": "The evidence files demonstrate thorough gate coverage: build evidence shows command output, spec compliance maps each acceptance criterion to implementation and test evidence with file:line references. The verdict includes reasoning, not just pass/fail. Score 0.8+ if all gates have evidence with specifics, 0.5-0.7 if evidence exists but is shallow, below 0.5 if evidence is missing or generic.",
          "target": ".specwright/work/test-work/evidence/spec-compliance.md",
          "description": "Evidence completeness and quality"
        }
      ],
      "tags": ["integration", "build-verify", "handoff"]
